Sun Pharmaceutical Gets U.S. FDA Approval for Ranitidine Syrup

-- B y   A d i   N a r a y a n
-- 
2011-09-23T05:46:38Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-23/sun-pharmaceutical-gets-u-s-fda-approval-for-ranitidine-syrup.html
Sun Pharmaceutical Industries Ltd. (SUNP) ,
 India ’s biggest drugmaker by market value, received approval
from the U.S. Food and Drug Administration for its ranitidine
hydrochloride syrup, the generic version of  GlaxoSmithKline
Plc (GSK) ’s Zantac heartburn medicine, according to a statement on the
regulator’s website.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Adi Narayan in Mumbai at 
 anarayan8@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Niveditha Ravi at 
 nravi2@bloomberg.net  